\id GLO - Kaluli Bible 
\mt1 To Haęž‰g Asulumaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ We  
\c 1  
\s1 A  
\p \k Aęž‰ibol\k* \tl (Abel, Abel)\tl* Aęž‰ibol e Adamaęž‰ ene soęž‰wa, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ene aowoęž‰ Kaęž‰in. Kaęž‰in eyoęž‰ ene ao Aęž‰iboloęž‰ sana sowoęž‰. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 4.1-8; Madi 23.35; Luk 11.51; Hibu 11.4, 12.24)  
\p \k Ablaham\k* \tl (Ablaham, Abraham) \tl* Ablaham eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ Isolael soęž‰loęž‰ mioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ emaęž‰muwoęž‰ e. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabuwaęž‰ iyayoęž‰ e. Gode eyoęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śGoęž‰noęž‰ henoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hen hoęž‰gi aęž‰na hamana,â€ť aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ e hen aęž‰na ane. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ Ablahamaęž‰ emaęž‰mui aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyaęž‰noęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ waga faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰iba aęž‰laęž‰liki, Ablaham oęž‰liaęž‰ nenelaki tolaęž‰len. Iyoęž‰ Godeya tilidaęž‰dalega, eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ oęž‰li tilidomaęž‰ib. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 15; Lom 4; Hibu 6.13-15; Song 105)  
\p \k Adam\k* \tl (Adam, Adam)\tl* Tamindeya Gode eyoęž‰ henoęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ Adamoęž‰ aęž‰na dimidoęž‰. Wi Adam aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ we, â€śE koęž‰le tamina faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.â€ť Adam oęž‰liaęž‰ ene inga If aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ goęž‰la baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale niloęž‰ amiloęž‰ aęž‰lab we aęž‰na moęž‰moęž‰da faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Mogagoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ tambo di. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 1-5; Luk 3.38; Lom 5.12-21; 1Kol 15.22,45; 1Tim 2.13-14; Yud 14)  
\p \k Alon\k* \tl (Fik, Fig)\tl* Isolael hen aęž‰namioęž‰ alonaęž‰ fowoęž‰ nudoęž‰ nafa koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ tulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ naęž‰sen. Koęž‰sega niliyoęž‰ fowoęž‰ moęž‰naki, foęž‰soęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ siaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ naęž‰sen. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 3.7, Madi 21.18-21, Luk 13.6-9)  
\p \k Ana\k* \tl (Anna, Anna)\tl* Ana e saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ e Godeyaęž‰ ene maliloęž‰ a aęž‰namioęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na diaęž‰len. E Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ Daęž‰feyoęž‰ Kalu miaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ yasilaęž‰li elen. E nuluwoęž‰loęž‰, hoęž‰lenowoęž‰loęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰li saęž‰sen. Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰liaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ hoęž‰len o aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ Maliloęž‰ aya diaęž‰gane koęž‰loęž‰, Ana oęž‰liaęž‰ Simeon oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰su saęž‰laęž‰li aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ sagalakiyoęž‰, Godemoęž‰ dulugu sioęž‰. (Luk 2.36-38)  
\p \k Ananaias\k* \tl (Ananias, Ananias) \tl* Ananaias oęž‰liaęž‰ ene inga Safaila oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ henoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ boęž‰ba dimiakiyoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ mole heboęž‰ inin woęž‰noęž‰le diaęž‰taki, heb nowoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dimiakiyoęž‰, Bidamoęž‰woęž‰ dikili sioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Bida dikidoęž‰ma, koęž‰sega Godeyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dikidoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰gabiki Gode eyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ sana sowoęž‰. (Ilig 5.1-11)  
\p \k Atemis\k* \tl (Artemis, Artemis)\tl* Atemis aęž‰noęž‰ madali godeyaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ oęž‰m. Aęž‰sia kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ emoęž‰ gulugululaki ene wiyoęž‰ duludaęž‰sen. Aęž‰fesaęž‰s amisaęž‰n aęž‰namioęž‰ Atemisaęž‰ wi duludakiloęž‰ gulugululaęž‰sen ayoęž‰ alan koęž‰loęž‰ dialifaęž‰. (Ilig 19.21-41)  
\s1 B  
\p \k Babilon\k* \tl (Babilon, Babylon)\tl* Babilon amisaęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ mada alan. Moęž‰luwoęž‰ Babilon iyoęž‰ Isolael oęž‰liaęž‰ bubaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Isolaeloęž‰ ili tinioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ modoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ Babilon ili taęž‰liaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Babilon hamanaęž‰ki dibodaki, aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ menaęž‰kiyoęž‰ fogoęž‰ moęž‰dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Isolael iyoęž‰ dona doęž‰laęž‰lowoęž‰ dom aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na sen. Yoęž‰n eyoęž‰ Babilon aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ gis kaluwoęž‰ oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰fe sioęž‰. (Mad 1.11, 12.17 Ilig 7.43, Kala 17-18)  
\p \k Bal\k* \tl (Bal, Baal)\tl* Bal aęž‰noęž‰ madali gode nowoęž‰ oęž‰m. Haęž‰laęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale Isolaelaęž‰ hen amiloęž‰ sen i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ madali gode Bal aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ wabudaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ ini Godeyoęž‰ taęž‰fomaęž‰ki iyoęž‰ dikidiyoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰gabiki, Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ ini Gode hendelemoęž‰loęž‰ gulugululaęž‰sen man aęž‰noęž‰ ka taęž‰taęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, madali gode Bal oęž‰moęž‰ gulugululaęž‰len. Ililoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰maęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, Gode e mada gadioęž‰woęž‰ alan dowaęž‰sen. (Lom 11.4)  
\p \k Bali\k* \tl (Bali, Barley) \tl* Bali fo aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰si oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, fo aęž‰noęž‰ tulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ basiab amioęž‰ falawa faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰sen. Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ falawa aęž‰noęž‰ soęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ naęž‰sen. (Lud 1-3; Yoęž‰n 6.9,13; Kala 6.6)  
\p \k Baęž‰ndikoęž‰s Hoęž‰len\k* \tl (Pentikos, Pentecost) \tl* Baęž‰ndikoęž‰s aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Gilig to koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ we, doęž‰laęž‰lowoęž‰ bilaęž‰foęž‰ oęž‰m. Isolael kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ sagaloęž‰ hoęž‰len nowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰fe sioęž‰. Tinioęž‰ Asuloęž‰ Hoęž‰len aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ aneyoęž‰, hoęž‰len doęž‰laęž‰lowoęž‰ bilaęž‰foęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰, Baęž‰ndikoęž‰s hoęž‰lenoęž‰ oęž‰m. Yu kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ imoęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, sagaloęž‰ hoęž‰len we daęž‰feyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ iliyoęž‰ boęž‰ba kelegoęž‰woęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dimiaęž‰sen.  
\m Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ Isolael kalu ili egeloęž‰ amioęž‰ widaęž‰ fo koęž‰loęž‰ kegene tumaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabiki, Gode eyoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, heb noloęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ Godemoęž‰ boba dimiaęž‰bi.  
\m Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ Hebene aęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene mamayoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleloęž‰wa mioęž‰ aęž‰na tindaęž‰gaęž‰ dowabikiyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene saęž‰soęž‰ aęž‰na moęž‰moęž‰doęž‰. (Ilig 2.1; 20.16; 1Kol 16.8)  
\p \k Bea\k* \tl (Bea, Bear)\tl* Bea aęž‰noęž‰ noęž‰ alan. Bea e noęž‰ halaidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, e gadiakiyoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ yasalaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ naęž‰sen. (Kala 13.2)  
\p \k Biaęž‰sibul\k* \tl (Belsebul, Beelzebul) \tl*Biaęž‰sibul wi aęž‰noęž‰ madali gode koęž‰loęž‰ Filistia kalu ililoęž‰ wabulu saęž‰laęž‰senoęž‰ oęž‰m. Wi aęž‰noęž‰ madali godeloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ ene wiyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰fe saęž‰laki wikiloęž‰. (Mad 12.24; Luk 11.13-19)  
\p \k Bobaloęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen i fofodoęž‰\k* \tl (Alta, Altar) \tl* Tamin amioęž‰ Yu kalu iliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ bobayoęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen. Iliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ soęž‰meakiyoęž‰ kao insoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ sibi insoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰, aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen. Moęž‰luwoęž‰ iliyoęž‰ uwoęž‰ dibidaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ imili alitakiyoęž‰ aęž‰na soęž‰meaęž‰sen, koęž‰sega tifa amioęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, iliyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ fofodaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, goęž‰l oęž‰liaęž‰ silba oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ waęž‰la ogaęž‰di alifaęž‰. Iliyoęž‰ dimidaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ diaęž‰siaęž‰likiyoęž‰, boba dimiab aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ waęž‰la diaęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 8.20, Yaęž‰m 2.21, Kala 11.1)  
\p \k Bobaloęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen kalu\k* \tl (Pris, Priest)\tl* Isolael kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene Maliloęž‰ A aęž‰namioęž‰ nanogoęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, i aęž‰noęž‰ bobaloęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen kalu aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen. Iyoęž‰ tambo Libaiyaęž‰ ene soęž‰loęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Iliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene maliloęž‰ a aęž‰noęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰likiyoęž‰, ililoęž‰ nanog alande dianoęž‰ Godemoęž‰loęž‰ boba soęž‰meaęž‰senoęž‰ oęž‰m. Donayoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰, ililoęž‰ bobaloęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰noęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ imilidaęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰fe alifelaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ tambo halaęž‰maęž‰kiyoęž‰, e Mada Maliloęž‰ Galalaęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ inaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰sen. Koęž‰sega hoęž‰len imilise amioęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso eyoęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ walaki dimi, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ene hoęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ tambo halaki dilaęž‰. (Hibu 5-10)  
\s1 D  
\p \k Daęž‰ibid\k* \tl (Devit, David)\tl* Isolaelaęž‰ ini misaęž‰ kalu alan nol us aęž‰namioęž‰, Daęž‰ibid e misaęž‰ kalu alan, waęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ e. Ene iyayoęž‰ Yaęž‰si, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰siyaęž‰ ene kalu sowa tifoęž‰ e. E misaęž‰ kalu alanoęž‰ oęž‰faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, tamin amioęž‰ eyoęž‰ ene iyayaęž‰ kabo sibi koęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰len. E oęž‰soęž‰wa ilikiyoęž‰, hoęž‰len no amioęž‰, e kalu alan wiloęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ bubaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ e sana sowoęž‰. Daęž‰ibid eyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ mada alan asulaęž‰sen. Eyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ wi dulubaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laki, gisaloęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Godeyaęž‰ ene Daęž‰feyoęž‰ kalu, Keliso e, Daęž‰ibidaęž‰ ene soęž‰loęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰liki, dinali saęž‰lan kalu iliyoęž‰ moęž‰luwoęž‰ saefaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tif amioęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ tambo ilili alifaęž‰. (Lom 1.3; Kala 22.16)  
\p \k Donki\k* \tl (Donki, Donkey) \tl* Donki aęž‰noęž‰ noęž‰ alan nowoęž‰ e. Isolael kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ donkiyoęž‰ fofaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, donki e amioęž‰ nanogoęž‰ alan dimidaęž‰sen. Kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰la diaęž‰tab amioęž‰, e diaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale iyoęž‰loęž‰ donki waęž‰l aęž‰na asitaęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰sen. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 16.12, Madi 21.5)  
\p \k Doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedean man\k* \tl (Katim skin bilong pikinini, Circumcision)\tl* Tamin amioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ Ablahamboęž‰loęž‰ to dinali saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ ele baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ we. Yu kalukaęž‰isale iyoęž‰ Gode amioęž‰ hendele tilidabukaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰li widakiyoęž‰, man we koęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰li mioęž‰. Man aęž‰noęž‰ we. Iliyoęž‰ kalu soęž‰wayoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰liaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hoęž‰len o faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰, soęž‰wa tuoęž‰lun aęž‰maęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeaęž‰sen. Koęž‰sega Yu kaluma iliyoęž‰ man oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidaęž‰len. Saęž‰soęž‰ hoęž‰gi faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰, Yu kalukaęž‰isalema i noloęž‰ Yaęž‰su amioęž‰ tilidabu, koęž‰sega iyoęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ moęž‰hege gedeaęž‰len. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Yu amiloęž‰ tilidabu kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ iyoęž‰ saęž‰s usamiloęž‰ miaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ kaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰. Koęž‰sega Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ moęž‰kaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ asulaki imoęž‰woęž‰ fanda widoęž‰. Tili dabu aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isale doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, Yu kalukaęž‰isalema doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ moęž‰hege gedeoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ iyoęž‰ tambo imiloęž‰ dowab. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 17.9-14)  
\s1 F  
\p \k Faęž‰lisi\k* \tl (Farisi, Pharisee)\tl* Faęž‰lisi kalu i we, Isolael kalukaęž‰isale i us aęž‰namioęž‰ wiloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ elen. Iliyoęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ fanda asululiaki, mada kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ele nol inidoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰baęž‰lakiyoęž‰, koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Faęž‰lisi kalu ini asulakiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ mada tininilaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulaki, ininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ kailaęž‰sen. Faęž‰lisi kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis dowaki, e sana somaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ togoęž‰ kedoęž‰.  
\s1 G  
\p \k Godeyaęž‰ Maliloęž‰ A Helebesoęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ Diaęž‰lenoęž‰\k* \tl (Haus sel bilong God, Tabernacle)\tl* Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, Gode e Isolael kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ ene ayoęž‰ dimaęž‰ki, Moęž‰saęž‰sboęž‰ widoęž‰. Eyoęž‰ a we diaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ manoęž‰ dinafa fanda widabikiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ a aęž‰noęž‰ noęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰f oęž‰liaęž‰ helebesoęž‰g oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ di. Gode e a aęž‰na dofoęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, bobaloęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen misaęž‰ kalu daęž‰feyoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ tinaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Godemoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na soęž‰kugulu meaęž‰sen. Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ haęž‰laęž‰ya siliki gulugululaęž‰sen.  
\m Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ kalaleli hen aęž‰na siaęž‰likiyoęž‰, no doęž‰goęž‰f dugu aęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo diaęž‰siaęž‰likiyoęž‰, ayoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ boęž‰boęž‰ge diaęž‰li siaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Isolaelaęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu Daęž‰ibid hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, iliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ maliloęž‰ a hendele aęž‰noęž‰ di koęž‰loęž‰, helebesoęž‰g a diaęž‰lowan aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰na edoęž‰.  
\p \k Godeyaęž‰ Maliloęž‰ A\k* \tl (Haus holi bilong God, Temple)\tl* Solomon hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, Isolael kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Maliloęž‰ A hendele aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰lusalem aęž‰na moęž‰moęž‰da dialifaęž‰. Tif amioęž‰ gis kalu noloęž‰ yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, a aęž‰noęž‰ bidilaęž‰. Hoęž‰len no amioęž‰ Saęž‰labaęž‰bul eyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Maliloęž‰ A nowoęž‰ waęž‰ka dialifaęž‰ koęž‰sega, aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰ bidilaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tif amioęž‰ Haęž‰lod eyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Maliloęž‰ Ayoęž‰ mada nafale nowoęž‰ aęž‰dialifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Yaęž‰suloęž‰ mioęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, a aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰elen. Isolael kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ a aęž‰na kegeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ widaki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ bobayoęž‰ aęž‰na soęž‰kugulu soęž‰meaęž‰len. Oęž‰goęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene maliloęž‰ ayoęž‰ oęž‰m. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ene Mamayoęž‰ ni usa sab.  
\p \k Godeyaęž‰ Sibi insoęž‰\k* \tl (Sipsip bilong God, Lamb of God)\tl* Yu kalu ili man amioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ ini mogagoęž‰woęž‰ hamaęž‰kiyoęž‰, sibi insoęž‰ nafa aęž‰noęž‰ saęž‰ndaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Godemoęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen. Sibiyaęž‰ hoęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ili mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰woęž‰ halab aęž‰namioęž‰, iyoęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ nafale maliloęž‰ dowaęž‰sen. Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ asuwaęž‰taki, ene melaęž‰noęž‰ ko dimi koęž‰loęž‰, e Godeyaęž‰ sibi insoęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰na daęž‰fe sioęž‰.  
\m Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰baęž‰le Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab i aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene sibi aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰. (Yoęž‰n 1.29,36)  
\p \k Godeyaęž‰ toloęž‰ dinali saęž‰lan kalu\k* \tl (Profet, Prophet)\tl* Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰loęž‰ kalab amiloęž‰ widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ e Godeyaęž‰ toloęž‰ dinali saęž‰lan kalu aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lan. Isolael hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale modoęž‰woęž‰ nanog aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰len. Nowoęž‰ Samuel, Elaiya, Natan, Aisaya, Yaęž‰limaya, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu modoęž‰ noloęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab. Iliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰i mioęž‰. Yaęž‰suloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, Yoęž‰n hoęž‰n amiloęž‰ toęž‰lolan aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ toloęž‰ dinali saęž‰lan kalu dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ toloęž‰ widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ toloęž‰ dinali saęž‰lan kalu aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lab.  
\p \k Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ Daęž‰feyoęž‰ Kalu\k* \tl (Krais, Christ) \tl* Isolael kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ hoęž‰gi dimiaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ gulalu mesea aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ wa hoęž‰noęž‰ kalu aęž‰maęž‰ misaęž‰ waęž‰la tulu alitaęž‰gaęž‰, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na dimaęž‰ki daęž‰feaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasilimaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ asulab aumboęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ aęž‰na daęž‰fe alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalu we wiyoęž‰ aęž‰na wikili alifaęž‰. Hibulu towaęž‰yoęž‰ â€śMaęž‰sayaâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gilig towaęž‰yoęž‰ â€śKelisoâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen. Keliso aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, haęž‰g noloęž‰ aęž‰lab. Nowoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ oęž‰m. Nowoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ Daęž‰feyoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ oęž‰m. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nowoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰lab.  
\s1 H  
\p \k Haęž‰foęž‰loęž‰ Dowan hoęž‰len\k* \tl (De Sabat, Sabbath)\tl* Moęž‰moęž‰doęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ we hoęž‰gi dimidakiyoęž‰, hoęž‰len doęž‰goęž‰felaęž‰foęž‰ us aęž‰namioęž‰, eyoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ tambo dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, aęž‰na edoęž‰. Hoęž‰len domaęž‰yoęž‰ e haęž‰foęž‰ dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, Yu kalukaęž‰isale iyoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki, eyoęž‰ eleyoęž‰ aęž‰na saefaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Haęž‰foęž‰loęž‰ Dowan hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ nanogoęž‰ mada moęž‰dimidaęž‰sen. Hibulu towaęž‰yoęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ â€śSabatâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen. Nililoęž‰ hoęž‰len doęž‰goęž‰fe saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Yu kalu iliyoęž‰ hoęž‰len domoęž‰ oęž‰m. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 2.1-3, Luk 6.1-11, 13.10-17, 14.1-5)  
\p \k Haęž‰ga\k* \tl (Hega, Hagar)\tl* Haęž‰ga e Ablahamaęž‰ inga Selayaęž‰ ene nanogdoęž‰ dian ga. Saęž‰la eyoęž‰ Ablahamboęž‰woęž‰ soęž‰wayoęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰laęž‰meaęž‰noęž‰ dowabikiyoęž‰, Saęž‰la eyoęž‰ Haęž‰ga aęž‰noęž‰ inboęž‰ dimaęž‰ki dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Haęž‰ga e Ablaham oęž‰liaęž‰ alilaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, e aęž‰na aleloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalu soęž‰wa Ismaeloęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰laęž‰li. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 16, 21.8-21, Gala 4.24-25)  
\p \k Haęž‰lod\k*  
\p 1. \k Haęž‰lod Alan\k*\tl (Helot, Herod the Great)\tl*Haęž‰lod Alan e Yaęž‰suloęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ Yudia hen aęž‰namiloęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu alan senoęž‰ e. Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ Lomaęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu iliyoęž‰ Yudia hen aęž‰noęž‰ ili boęž‰foęž‰len. Haęž‰lod e Yu kalu koęž‰sega e Lomaęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu i oęž‰liaęž‰ ege dowabiki, iliyoęž‰ e Yudia hen aęž‰noęž‰ e boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰. Haęž‰lod eyoęž‰ hen eloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kalu nomaęž‰yoęž‰ diabenaęž‰kiyoęž‰ e tagilaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Yaęž‰suloęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, Haęž‰lod eyoęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu hoęž‰gi nowoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰liakaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, eyoęž‰ kalu soęž‰wa tuoęž‰lun aęž‰noęž‰ tambo yasalaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saefaęž‰. (Madi 2.1-22, Luk 1.5)  
\p 2. \k Haęž‰lod Antibas\k* \tl (Helot Antipas, Herod Antipas)\tl* Haęž‰lod Antibas e Haęž‰lod Alan aęž‰maęž‰ ene soęž‰wa. Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ towoęž‰ widaki, molo haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰len hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, kalu wemaęž‰yoęž‰ Galili hen aęž‰noęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰len. Ga Haęž‰lodias aęž‰noęž‰ e di koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ Yoęž‰n hoęž‰n amiloęž‰ toęž‰lolan kalu aęž‰noęž‰ sana sowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yu kalu iliyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ sana somaęž‰noęž‰ dowabikiyoęž‰, Haęž‰lod Antibas eyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ moęž‰waliloęž‰. (Mak 6.14-29, Luk 23.6-12)  
\p 3. \k Haęž‰lod Agiliba \k* \tl (Helot Agiliba, Herod Agribba)\tl* Haęž‰lod Agiliba e Haęž‰lod Alan aęž‰maęž‰ ene emaęž‰mu. Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ saęž‰soęž‰ hoęž‰gi moęž‰moęž‰dabikiyoęž‰, kalu Haęž‰lod Agiliba eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ mada dikidoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu wemaęž‰yoęž‰ Yoęž‰naęž‰ ene ao Yaęž‰maęž‰soęž‰ sana sowoęž‰. (Ilig 12.1-23)  
\p 4. \k Haęž‰lod Agiliba 2 \k* \tl (Helot Agiliba 2, Herod Agribba 2)\tl* Haęž‰lod Agiliba 2 e Haęž‰lod Agiliba aęž‰maęž‰ ene soęž‰wa. Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Foloęž‰ moęž‰walilab amioęž‰, kalu wemaęž‰yoęž‰ alobana baęž‰baęž‰. (Ilig 25.13 - 26.2, 26.19, 27-32)  
\p \k Hibulu\k* \tl (Hibru, Hebrew)\tl* Hibulu aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ to wiyoęž‰ oęž‰m. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ Hibulu kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen. Ili wi nowoęž‰ Yu. Kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ Ablahamaęž‰ esoęž‰loęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale ililoęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ Hibulu to aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen.  
\s1 I  
\p \k Iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu\k* \tl (Aposel, Apostle) \tl* Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰, e kudu menaęž‰kiyoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ kugulaęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰. Iyoęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰ siaęž‰likiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ to widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ tilidaęž‰daki kudu haęž‰naęž‰len. Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ to manoęž‰ imoęž‰ widaęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, iyoęž‰ asululiabikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰ hen nowa siaęž‰liki kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ walamaęž‰ki iligaęž‰feloęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ iyoęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰. Iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, Gilig towaęž‰yoęž‰ â€śAbasolâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lan. I aęž‰noęž‰, saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu dowoęž‰. (Madi 10.1-4, Mak 3.13-19, Luk 6.12-16)  
\p \k Isolael\k* \tl (Israel, Israel) \tl* Aisaęž‰g diaęž‰ Laęž‰baęž‰ga liaęž‰maęž‰ soęž‰wa imili nowoęž‰ Yaęž‰kob. Yaęž‰kob e kalu dowabiki, e Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ buboęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ e wi hoęž‰gi nowoęž‰ dimiaki, Isolael wikiloęž‰. Eyoęž‰ kalu soęž‰wayoęž‰ kugulaęž‰foęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li koęž‰loęž‰, i aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ Isolael soęž‰loęž‰ kugulaęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Tif amioęž‰ Isolaelaęž‰ emaęž‰mu i aęž‰noęž‰ tambo Isolael kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lan.  
\s1 K  
\p \k Kalule Dowoęž‰\k* \tl (Pikinini Bilong Man, Son of Man) \tl* Yaęž‰su e Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa koęž‰loęž‰ e Gode. Koęž‰sega e Hebeneyoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, henfeloęž‰ wenamioęž‰ e wiloęž‰ma kalu domaęž‰ni tindakiyoęž‰, e henfeloęž‰ soęž‰wale oęž‰ngoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li. E henfeloęž‰ kalule faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, e â€śKalule Dowoęž‰â€ť wi aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ di. Wi aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰g aęž‰noęž‰, imiloęž‰ koęž‰m, Godeyaęž‰ Daęž‰feyoęž‰ Kalu. (Mak 10.33,45, Luk 19.10)  
\p \k Kaęž‰mol\k* \tl (Kamel, Camel)\tl* Noęž‰ kaęž‰mol e mada alan koęž‰loęž‰, ene felaęž‰kiyoęž‰ mada sasal. Hidaęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ e waęž‰la diaęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, kalaleli hen aęž‰namioęž‰ e henoęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰li ka diaęž‰haęž‰naęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ e waęž‰l amioęž‰ oęž‰li asitaęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰sen. (Madi 3.4, 19.24, Mak 10.25, Luk 18.25)  
\p \k Keliso kalukaęž‰isale\k* \tl (Kristen, Christian)\tl* Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su emoęž‰loęž‰ fogaęž‰le saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ nodolaki, man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ faęž‰s dimiab aęž‰noęž‰, iyoęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰sen. Kalukaęž‰isale i we Yaęž‰su amioęž‰ tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ ene man aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ iliyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene wiyoęž‰ aęž‰na di. Antioęž‰g amisaęž‰n aęž‰namioęž‰ saęž‰soęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰namiloęž‰ sab aęž‰noęž‰ â€śKeliso kalukaęž‰isaleâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰na moęž‰moęž‰da wikiloęž‰. (Ilig 26.28, 1Bid 4.16)  
\s1 L  
\p \k Lasalas\k* \tl (Laselas, Lazarus) \tl* Lasalas e Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene mili kalu nowoęž‰ e. Malia oęž‰liaęž‰ Mada oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ aowoęž‰ e. Lasalas e walaf baęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, ado aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ menaęž‰ki hoęž‰idoęž‰. Yaęž‰su e aęž‰na haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Lasalasoęž‰ oęž‰ma dali alifaęž‰loęž‰biki baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰sega, Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ e aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alifaęž‰. (Yoęž‰n 11.1-44)  
\p \k Laęž‰baęž‰ga\k* \tl (Rebeka, Rebekah)\tl* Laęž‰baęž‰ga e, Ablahamaęž‰ kalu soęž‰wa Aisaęž‰gaęž‰ ingayaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ oęž‰m. Eyoęž‰ soęž‰wayoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰, Isoęž‰ diaęž‰ Yaęž‰kob diaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li. Yaęž‰kob eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ Isolael soęž‰loęž‰ kugulaęž‰foęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ inuwoęž‰ Laęž‰baęž‰ga. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 24 - 27, Lom 9.10-13)  
\p \k Lehab\k* \tl (Rahap, Rehab) \tl* Isolael kalu aęž‰laęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ Kaęž‰inaęž‰n henoęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰nikiloęž‰ oęž‰lusen ane aęž‰namioęž‰, gis kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ iyoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ yasalaęž‰maęž‰nigabiki, Lehab eyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ asuwaęž‰taki, woęž‰noęž‰le taęž‰foęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, keaęž‰fo nuluwoęž‰ fufaloęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰gulu aęž‰na tinaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, haęž‰laęž‰ya hamanaęž‰ki iligaęž‰foęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Kenan kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰ bubab amioęž‰, iliyoęž‰ Lehab oęž‰liaęž‰ ene soęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰sana sowoęž‰. Lehab e Isolael ga faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Lehab eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, tif amioęž‰ Daęž‰ibid oęž‰liaęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. (Madi 1.5, Hibu 11.31, Yaęž‰m 2.25)  
\p \k Lesol\k* \tl (Resel, Rachel)\tl* Lesol e Yaęž‰kobaęž‰ ingayoęž‰ nowoęž‰ e. Yaęž‰kob eyoęž‰ Lesol e mada alan asulaęž‰sen. E Yosaęž‰b oęž‰liaęž‰ Baęž‰nsamen oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ anowoęž‰ e. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 29 - 35, Madi 2.18)  
\s1 M  
\p \k Madali nanog dian kalu\k* \tl (Wokboi nating, Slave) \tl* Madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu aęž‰noęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu nomaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki, nanogoęž‰ eloęž‰ saęž‰lab au dimidaęž‰sen. Misaęž‰ kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ iyoęž‰ moleyaęž‰ kililiaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, iliyoęž‰ inin asuloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib. Iliyoęž‰ ini misaęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au ka kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Keliso kalukaęž‰isale ili misaęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ Yaęž‰su koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ eloęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰naki, iyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene madali nanog dian kalukaęž‰isale dowoęž‰. (1Kol 7.20-24, Aęž‰fes 6.5-9, Kolo 3.22-25)  
\p \k Mana\k* \tl (Mana, Manna)\tl* Moęž‰luwoęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Isib henoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, maęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ma kalaleli hena haęž‰nabikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰gi nowoęž‰ imoęž‰ maiyaęž‰ki dimi. Hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo iyoęž‰ kalaleli hena siaęž‰labikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene dimidaliaęž‰gaęž‰ dimiaęž‰len. Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰daęž‰sen. Iliyoęž‰ maęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ mana aęž‰laęž‰wikiloęž‰. Hibulu towaęž‰loęž‰ Mana aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, nili towaęž‰yoęž‰ â€śWe oęž‰baęž‰?â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lab. (Yoęž‰n 6.31,49, Hibulu 9.4, Kala 2.17)  
\p \k Maęž‰kisedeg\k* \tl (Melkisedek, Melchizedek)\tl* Maęž‰kisedeg e Godemoęž‰loęž‰ bobaloęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen kalu nowoęž‰ e. Ablaham eyoęž‰ Lodoęž‰ asuwaęž‰taki gis kalu nol oęž‰liaęž‰ bubaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ yaęž‰len amioęž‰, Maęž‰kisedeg e usa galili. Maęž‰kisedeg eyoęž‰ Ablahamoęž‰ dinafa meseaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu sioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Ablaham eyoęž‰ bubaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ gis kaluwaęž‰ kelegoęž‰ eloęž‰ di aęž‰noęž‰, heb doęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Maęž‰kisedegboęž‰ dimi. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 14.17-24, Hibu 5 - 7)  
\p \k Maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu\k* \tl (Ensol, Angel)\tl* Maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu iyoęž‰ Hebene halona iliki, Godeyaęž‰ nanog dimidaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wena yaęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰sen. Maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ma, iyoęž‰ mama koęž‰loęž‰ sab. Taminde amioęž‰ maęž‰mulaęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ tambo Hebene sen koęž‰sega, imili nomaęž‰yoęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ yoęž‰le dowaki aęž‰laęž‰iyoęž‰. Ene wiyoęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰gabiki Gode eyoęž‰ e oęž‰lugaęž‰foęž‰. Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ maęž‰mulaęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ alobaęž‰daki, noloęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ haęž‰ga oęž‰doęž‰waki, noloęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ dowoęž‰. Maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰loęž‰ kudu ane aęž‰noęž‰, niliyoęž‰ mama mogagoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lab. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 3.24, Luk 1.19,26, Ilig 12.6-11, 27.23, Hibu 1.14)  
\p \k Moęž‰saęž‰s\k* \tl (Moses, Moses)\tl* Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Isib hen aęž‰na sen amioęž‰, Isib kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ iyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰labikiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ Isibaęž‰ ili madali nanog dian kalukaęž‰isale dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰gabikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale enedoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asuwaęž‰taki aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasilimaęž‰kiyoęž‰, kalu nowoęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰. Kalu aęž‰noęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰s. Moęž‰saęž‰s eyoęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isale koęž‰loęž‰ Isib hen amiloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ diaęž‰likiloęž‰ sen aęž‰noęž‰, tililiaęž‰gaęž‰ Kaęž‰inaęž‰n hen aęž‰na ane. Iyoęž‰ Kaęž‰inaęž‰n hena haęž‰nab amioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ene eleyoęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰sboęž‰ dimi.  
\s1 Oęž‰  
\p \k Oęž‰lif\k* \tl (Olif, Olive)\tl* Oęž‰lif aęž‰noęž‰ i wiyoęž‰ oęž‰m. I aęž‰noęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isale ili gelaęž‰sen. Iliyoęž‰ i fo aęž‰noęž‰ naęž‰sen, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ fo noloęž‰ basiaki, oęž‰waęž‰l hoęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰na diaęž‰sen. (Lom 11.17,24, Yaęž‰m 3.12, Kala 11.4)  
\s1 S  
\p \k Sadusi kalu\k* \tl (Sadyusi, Sadducees)\tl* Sadusi kalu i we, Isolael kalukaęž‰isale i us aęž‰na wiloęž‰ di kalu koęž‰loęž‰ elen. Sadusi kalu i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ fanda asululiaki, mada kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Iyoęž‰ Faęž‰lisi kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰, koęž‰sega Faęž‰lisi oęž‰liaęž‰ Sadusi oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ mada alan kegaęž‰sen. Moęž‰woęž‰ Faęž‰lisi kalu iliyoęž‰ dane ane kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ tif ami aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasimaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰ tili asuloęž‰, koęž‰sega Sadusi kalu iliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰tili asuloęž‰. Sadusi oęž‰liaęž‰ Faęž‰lisi kalu oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰sumoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰beakiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilise dowaki, Yaęž‰su saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ togoęž‰ kedaęž‰len. (Madi 22.23, Ilig 23.6-8)  
\p \k Sagalaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ Falawa Mosoloęž‰ dowoęž‰faęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len\k* \tl (Bikpela De Bilong Bret I No Gat Yis, Feast of Unleavened Bread) \tl* Donayoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰, Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Tinioęž‰ Asuloęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ edab amioęž‰, Sagalaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ Falawa Mosoloęž‰ dowoęž‰faęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, iyoęž‰ sagalaki kegeaęž‰sen. Soęž‰goęž‰ ageloęž‰ imilise us aęž‰namioęž‰, iliyoęž‰ falawaloęž‰ anayan kelegoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰diaęž‰taki, falawa mosowoęž‰ sodaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ naęž‰sen. Ililoęž‰ aęž‰namiloęž‰ kegeab aęž‰noęž‰ Isib hen amiloęž‰ gaęž‰liloęž‰ sili alifaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulaki dimidaęž‰sen. (Kisim 12.14-20, Madi 26.17, Luk 22.1)  
\p \k Sainai\k* \tl (Sainai, Sinai)\tl* Sainai aęž‰noęž‰ hen misioęž‰. Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Isib hen aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, iyoęž‰ Sainai misioęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Moęž‰saęž‰soęž‰ Sainai misioęž‰wa haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Godeyoęž‰ aęž‰na gidoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰na sen amioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ele doęž‰laęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ u ami saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, emoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na dimi. (Kisim 19-20, Gala 4.21-31)  
\p \k Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰\k* \tl (Satan, Satan)\tl* Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ e mama mogagoęž‰ nol koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ sab oęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰ misaęž‰ alanoęž‰ e. Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ e Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale Godeloęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab i oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ gis alandoęž‰ diaęž‰laboęž‰ e. Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidamaęž‰kiyoęž‰ eyoęž‰ dikidaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ madali toloęž‰ saęž‰lan aęž‰maęž‰ iyayoęž‰ e. (Luk 10.18, Yoęž‰n 12.31, 2Kol 4.4, Kala 12.7-9, 20.2)  
\p \k Sibiloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu\k* \tl (Wasman bilong sipsip, Shepherd) \tl* Sibiloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu iliyoęž‰ sibi boęž‰foęž‰liki, fugus nafa oęž‰liaęž‰ hoęž‰n nafa oęž‰liaęž‰ maiyaęž‰kiyoęž‰, kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ sibiyoęž‰ tililiaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, henoęž‰ nafaya taęž‰taki boęž‰foęž‰lowaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ sibiyoęž‰ saila gasayaęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰ni yabenaęž‰ki boęž‰foęž‰lowan. Yaęž‰suloęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ sibiloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu noloęž‰ amisaęž‰n haęž‰laęž‰ya sibi boęž‰foęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suloęž‰wa yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, e wabudaki Godemoęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ e amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ sibi oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowaęž‰sen. (Luk 2.7-20, Yoęž‰n 10.11, 1Bid 5.2)  
\p \k Sodom\k* \tl (Sodom, Sodom)\tl* Sodom aęž‰noęž‰ amisaęž‰n wiyoęž‰ oęž‰m. Lod e amisaęž‰n aęž‰na haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Sodom anib amiloęž‰ elenoęž‰ amisaęž‰n nowoęž‰ Gomola. Amisaęž‰n aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ alan dimidaęž‰labiki, Gode eyoęž‰ amisaęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ tambo yasalaęž‰. (Moęž‰moęž‰ 18-19, Madi 10.15, 11.23-24, Luk 17.29, Kala 11.8)  
\s1 T  
\p \k Tili widaęž‰sen kalu\k* \tl (Disaipel, Disciple)\tl* Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nakiloęž‰ to eloęž‰ widab amiloęž‰ tili daęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰, tili widaęž‰sen kaluwoęž‰ i oęž‰m. Yaęž‰su e henfeloęž‰ wena silikiyoęž‰, kalu kugulaęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, i aęž‰noęž‰ eloęž‰ tili widaęž‰sen kalu aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lan. Yaęž‰su e Hebene aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ ane aęž‰namioęž‰, Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ tambo enedoęž‰ tili widaęž‰sen kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen. Aęž‰maęž‰ faęž‰s amioęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ â€śKelisoâ€ť wiyoęž‰ aęž‰na di. (Madi 10.1-4, Ilig 11.26)  
\p \k Tinioęž‰ Asuloęž‰ Maęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len\k* \tl (Bikpela De Bilong Tingim De God i larim Israel i Stap Gut, Passover)\tl* Donayoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰, Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ i asufaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ sagalaki kegeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na naęž‰sen. Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Isibdoęž‰ sen aęž‰noęž‰, iyoęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ sili alifaęž‰. Iyoęž‰ sili alifaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Isibaęž‰loęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰b soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰li aęž‰noęž‰ tambo yasalaęž‰maęž‰nikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śGioęž‰ sibiyoęž‰ saęž‰ndaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hoęž‰boęž‰woęž‰ wasuliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, tog amiloęž‰ sowaęž‰kif oęž‰liaęž‰ kea oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰na mululaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰lalega, Godeyaęž‰ ene maęž‰mul kaluwoęž‰ yakiyoęž‰, hoęž‰boęž‰woęž‰ baęž‰dalikiyoęž‰, a aęž‰noęž‰ tiniaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰ibâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dona tambo amioęž‰, Isolael kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰asulakiyoęž‰, maęž‰noęž‰ maęž‰nikiyoęž‰ aęž‰na kegeaęž‰sen. (Kisim 12, Madi 26.2,5,17-19)  
\s1 W  
\p \k Wain hoęž‰n\k* \tl (Wain, Wine)\tl* Wain i aęž‰noęž‰ me oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ uwoęž‰lakiyoęž‰, fowoęž‰ geneloęž‰ helemaęž‰ib. Isolael kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ fowoęž‰ tulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, u waęž‰la basiaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, hoęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰na diaęž‰sen. Hoęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰foęž‰lab amioęž‰, wain hoęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰sen. Wain hoęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ iliyoęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ naęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ wain fo noloęž‰ iliyoęž‰ tulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, ofa diaęž‰foęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, kalaliliaba naęž‰sen. (Yoęž‰n 15, Madi 21.33-43)  
\p \k Wit\k* \tl (Wit, Wheat)\tl* Isolael kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ wit fo aęž‰noęž‰ gelan. Wit fo aęž‰noęž‰ hedab amioęž‰, iliyoęž‰ gedeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, fo aęž‰noęž‰ kegeneliaęž‰ diaęž‰taęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ fo aęž‰noęž‰ u alanaęž‰ waęž‰la basiaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, mu faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰ falawa dimidaęž‰sen. Falawa aęž‰noęž‰ iliyoęž‰ sodaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ naęž‰sen. Bali fo aęž‰noęž‰ witaęž‰ fo oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰.  
\s1 Y  
\p \k Yaęž‰si\k* \tl (Jesi, Jessi) \tl* Yaęž‰siyoęž‰ Daęž‰ibidaęž‰ iyayoęž‰ oęž‰m. (Madi 1.5-6, Luk 3.32, Ilig 13.22, Lom 15.12)  
\p \k Yaęž‰su\k* \tl (Jisas, Jesus) \tl* Yaęž‰su e Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰wa. Yaęž‰su wi aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ we, eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ asuwaęž‰taki gasiliaęž‰sen. Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene wiyoęž‰ nowoęž‰ we, Yaęž‰su Keliso, Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa, Kalule Dowoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Daęž‰ibidaęž‰ ene e maęž‰mu.  
\p \k Yaęž‰su Asuloęž‰ Maęž‰noęž‰\k* \tl (Kaikai bilong Bikpela, Communion) \tl*Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ kegeakiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su sowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asulaki, wain hoęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰ falawa dowoęž‰faęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ naęž‰sen. Wain hoęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene hoęž‰boęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰m. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ falawa dowoęž‰faęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰m. Yaęž‰su e oęž‰sana somaęž‰noęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, enedoęž‰ tiliwidaęž‰sen kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ siliki maęž‰noęž‰ naęž‰likiyoęž‰, imoęž‰woęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki walalifaęž‰.  
\p \k Yis\k* \tl (Yis, Yeast) \tl* Yis aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ falawayoęž‰ anamaęž‰ki diaęž‰tan. Yis haęž‰lu aęž‰noęž‰ falawa oęž‰liaęž‰ woęž‰gelaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰b amioęž‰, falawa aęž‰noęž‰ mada alan domaęž‰ib. Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ yis aęž‰na bale saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ haęž‰lulaęž‰su aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ mada alan faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰liki widoęž‰. (Madi 13.33, 16.6,12, 1Kol 5.6-8, Gala 5.9)  
\p \k Yoęž‰sua\k* \tl (Josua, Joshua)\tl* Moęž‰saęž‰s e sowab amioęž‰, Yoęž‰sua e Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleloęž‰ tililiaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ Kaęž‰inaęž‰n hen aęž‰na tililiaęž‰gane. Hen aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ Isolaelaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰ saefaęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰m. Isolael kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ hen us aęž‰na tinaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Iliyoęž‰ hendoęž‰ bisoęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ bubaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ tinioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, hen aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰na di. Yoęž‰sua eyoęž‰ hen aęž‰noęž‰ alobaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Isolael soęž‰loęž‰ kugulaęž‰foęž‰ oęž‰moęž‰ heb heb aęž‰laęž‰dimiaęž‰i ane. Koęž‰sega Libai soęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰sen kalu dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, hen aęž‰noęž‰ heboęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰alobana me. (Ilig 7.45, Hibu 4.8)  
\p \k Yu Kalukaęž‰isale\k* \tl (Yuda, Jew)\tl* Ablahamaęž‰ ene maęž‰mui taęž‰i mioęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen. ABLAHAM to aęž‰noęž‰ boęž‰ba. Tamin amioęž‰, to Yu aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ we, kalukaęž‰isale Yuda hen amiloęž‰ senoęž‰ oęž‰m. Kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰, Ablahamaęž‰ kalu soęž‰wa Yuda eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰m. Koęž‰sega tif amioęž‰ Yu wi aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isale tambowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feaki sioęž‰. ISOLAEL to aęž‰noęž‰ boęž‰ba.  